---
layout: base.njk
title: "Checkin to Checkout — The E-Commerce Podcast"
description: "Stories from e-commerce leaders on how they got where they are, and where they think the industry is going. Hosted by Justin Aronstein."
---

<div class="podcast-index">

  <div class="podcast-index__header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="podcast-index__hero">
        {% if podcast.metadata.image %}
        <img class="podcast-index__cover" src="{{ podcast.metadata.image }}" alt="Checkin to Checkout Podcast Cover" width="200" height="200" />
        {% endif %}
        <div class="podcast-index__info">
          <p class="podcast-index__eyebrow">The Podcast</p>
          <h1 class="podcast-index__title">Checkin to Checkout</h1>
          <p class="podcast-index__description">{{ podcast.metadata.description }}</p>
          {% include "components/podcast-platforms.njk" %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="podcast-index__episodes">
    <div class="container">
      {% if podcast.seasons.length %}

      {% for season in podcast.seasons %}
      <div class="season-group">
        <h2 class="season-heading">Season {{ season.number }}</h2>
        <div class="episode-list">
          {% for ep in season.episodes %}
          <a href="/podcast/{{ ep.slug }}/" class="episode-card">
            {% if ep.image %}
            <img class="episode-card__img" src="{{ ep.image }}" alt="{{ ep.title }}" width="96" height="96" loading="lazy" />
            {% endif %}
            <div class="episode-card__body">
              <div class="episode-card__meta">
                <span class="episode-card__num">Ep. {{ ep.episodeNum }}</span>
                <span class="episode-card__sep">·</span>
                <span>{{ ep.readableDate }}</span>
                {% if ep.duration %}<span class="episode-card__sep">·</span><span>{{ ep.duration }}</span>{% endif %}
              </div>
              <h3 class="episode-card__title">{{ ep.title }}</h3>
              {% if ep.plainDescription %}
              <p class="episode-card__desc">{{ ep.plainDescription | truncate(160) }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <div class="episode-card__arrow">→</div>
          </a>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}

      {% else %}
      <p style="color: var(--text-muted); padding: 3rem 0;">Episodes loading — check back soon.</p>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="podcast-guest-cta">
        <p class="podcast-guest-cta__text">Want to share your story on Checkin to Checkout?</p>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark" data-podcast-modal>Apply to Be a Guest →</button>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>
